An experimental block driver for having fun
 
=====
Compile:
	$ make
Install:
	$ sudo make install
destall:
	$ sudo make destall
reinstall:
	$ sudo reinstall

=====
Current status:
   1. A device called 'blockdevice0' will show up at /dev/ dir after we install
      this module. Functions to deal with I/O requests are not implemented yet.
